lang pension scheme of Haryana Labour Welfare Board, welfare fund provides Rs. 3,000 per month as assistance to disabled laborers. The terms and conditions to avail Haryana Labour Handicap Pension Yojana are as follows:-", "002-table": {"row": 5, "column": 1, "data": [["Eligibility / \u092a\u093e\u0924\u094d\u0930\u0924\u093e"], ["Membership Years / \u0938\u0926\u0938\u094d\u092f\u0924\u093e \u0935\u0930\u094d\u0937", "1"], ["Apply Frequency / \u0906\u0935\u0947\u0926\u0928 \u0915\u0940 \u0938\u0940\u092e\u093e", "1"], ["Scheme For / \u0907\u0938 \u092f\u094b\u091c\u0928\u093e \u0915\u0947 \u0932\u093f\u090f", "All"], ["Continue After Death / \u092e\u0943\u0924\u094d\u092f\u0941 \u0915\u0947 \u092c\u093e\u0926 \u091c\u093e\u0930\u0940", "No"]]}, "003-normal": "Labour Welfare Fund Haryana Viklang Pension Scheme 2019 is available for all registered workers of the Haryana state who are suffering from infectious diseases or got disabled at worksite."}, "005-section": {"000-title": "Haryana Labour Disabled Pension Scheme for Persons with Disabilities Conditions", "001-normal": "People can follow the below mentioned conditions to avail financial aid under Labour Welfare Board Disabled Pension Scheme in Haryana:-", "002-listElement": "- All the labourers must be registered with at-least 1 year membership / subscription.", "003-listElement": "- In the identity certificate of the registered laborers, registration fees and updated subscription amount is to be mentioned.", "004-listElement": "- Candidates must produced Disability Certificate (70% to 100% permanent disability) issued by the Health department of Haryana.", "005-normal": "All the disabled persons needs to apply online within 1 year of occuring of disability.", "006-normal": "Source / Reference Link: hrylabour.gov.in"}}